{"tid":780954,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果今日陳浩天講洗獨係踏紅線，當日陳巧文講藏獨又唔見話踏到條紅線","createTime":"2018-08-15T13:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T11:10:58.000Z","uid":60057,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d77c03096e224a4ea03736b678daa63fc6ae0e8c","tid":780954,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"03年話立23條都大大聲講到話講同討論係無問題，都搞到全港50萬人上街<br />\n<br />\n08年陳巧文嗌藏獨就唔係分裂國家？你今時今日先黎話條紅線係唔可以講？<br />\n<br />\n18年23條都未立就變左公開演講叫踏紅線，咁28年我估有咁既諗法既人就係踏紅線，38年應該potentially 會諗既就踏紅線。<br />\n<br />\n條紅線真係好flexible。彈出彈入你吹得我漲。"},{"pid":"e752e1e05913cb28719cfed8d1c19909a3b21ad8","tid":780954,"uid":55770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"踩"},{"pid":"2d239460d6ca3c1fa1d65ece3b7e26b187549748","tid":780954,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e752e1e05913cb28719cfed8d1c19909a3b21ad8","tid":780954,"uid":55770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"踩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"一時醒唔起，唔該巴打"},{"pid":"449e65fb6f0ba8f7a2ef8af89b6986632ae8749e","tid":780954,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"當年全民屌鳩陳巧文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae1417457439324b31e244bc5560624c092ac10","tid":780954,"uid":20170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"當年梁國雄夠衝出嚟撐陳巧文啦<br />\n今日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中共條「紅線」識郁是常識 不如睇真啲班泛民仲好過"},{"pid":"305a7e8bddefacd1f5339a16d2518a3f072b8e51","tid":780954,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T03:07:25.000Z","msg":"當年陳巧文被港豬瘋狂圍屌, 真係陰功<br />\n<br />\n明明佢係講得無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/f